reviewtext: I like the product, however after doing some research I found what I believe to be the EXACT same reel at sears for $24.95. I actually purchased one from Sears when they were offering it for $18 and some change. The construction is identical but the one from Sears does not have a circuit breaker, to me that's not a big deal.  Other then that so far it works like I expected it to.
